Name: django-werkzeug-debugger-runserver
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Replaces Django's runserver command with one that includes the Werkzeug debugger (shamelessly ripped out off django-extensions)
Home-page: http://github.com/philippbosch/django-werkzeug-debugger-runserver
Author: Philipp Bosch and https://github.com/django-extensions/django-extensions/contributors
Author-email: hello@pb.io
License: BSD
Description: django-werkzeug-debugger-runserver
        ==================================
        
        This app extracts the ``runserver_plus``_ management command from 
        django-extensions_ and makes it available as a replacement for Django's
        default ``runserver`` management command.
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install from PyPI::
        
            pip install django-werkzeug-debugger-runserver
        
        
        Configuration
        -------------
        
        Edit your ``settings.py`` and include ``werkzeug_debugger_runserver`` in your
        ``INSTALLED_APPS``
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = (
                â€¦,
                'werkzeug_debugger_runserver',
            )
        
        
        .. _django-extensions: https://github.com/django-extensions/django-extensions/
        .. _runserver_plus: http://packages.python.org/django-extensions/runserver_plus.html
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
